data.description: WONDERFUL STARTER HOME! Cute 3 bedroom 1 bath home near the greenbelt and river.  Tiled entry to laminate flooring in living room and hallway.  Kitchen is tiled as well as the bathroom floor and tub surround.  Some new vinyl windows in home.  Crown molding in bedrooms and living room.  Large entry closed and newer driveway. Some closets have built in shelves. Basement is mostly for storage and has concrete floors.  Wood stove in living room but additional hearth is needed in front.  Roof looks in good condition and it has a nice deck in the fenced backyard.  Owner's prefer to sell this AS-IS or buyers to do the work to get it to Government financing standards.  Cracked and peeling paint on eaves is being worked on.  Wood stove may need to be removed.  Gas wall unit in living room and electric cadet has been added to bedrooms.
